\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Such issues are byond good manners.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Put your faith in god,}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 And put your sword in their belly! - my twist}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Hope these gallant generals of hol and manchester had taken up with the enemy, for then we\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d have a surer chance at victory. For by their reluctance to pursue this war with the intesity that it demands, that have proved themselves treachorous to our cause and to this nation.}
